Richard T. DORMAN, Appellant, v. STATE OF GEORGIA et al., Appellees. No. 25316. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. April 22, 1968. Richard T. Dorman, pro se. Mathew Robins, Asst. Atty. Gen., Atlanta, Ga., for appellees.

Before WISDOM, BELL and DYER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment is affirmed. Henderson v. Circuit Court, 5 Cir. 1968, 392 F.2d 551 [decided on April 22, 1968].
